‚úÖ **Phase 2: Secure Codebase** (SAST, SCA, GitLeaks, DAST).  
‚úÖ **Phase 3: Secure Containers** (Trivy, Kube-bench).  
‚úÖ **Phase 4: Secure Applications** (OWASP Top 10, Threat Modeling).  

